<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q11_v9" title="Q11_v9" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En una imprenta se utiliza una tarjeta de fórmula para calcular cuántas hojas se necesitan para imprimir un folleto.</p>
    <div>
      <p>La tarjeta indica la siguiente relación entre las cantidades:
        <m:math>
          <m:mi>H</m:mi>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>12</m:mn>
          <m:mo>·</m:mo>
          <m:mi>e</m:mi>
        </m:math>,
        donde
        <m:math>
          <m:mi>e</m:mi>
        </m:math>
        es el número de ejemplares del folleto y H es la cantidad total de hojas necesarias.
      </p>
    </div>
    <p>Cada resma contiene
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>500</m:mn>
      </m:math>
      hojas.</p>
    <p>Si se deben imprimir
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>750</m:mn>
      </m:math>
      ejemplares de un folleto, ¿cuántas resmas de papel se necesitan como mínimo?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">9 000 resmas<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Con <m:math><m:mi>e</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn></m:math>, la fórmula da <m:math><m:mi>H</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> hojas, no 9 000 resmas. Como cada resma tiene <m:math><m:mn>500</m:mn></m:math> hojas, se necesitan <m:math><m:mn>9&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math> resmas.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">1,5 resmas<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Para <m:math><m:mi>e</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn></m:math>, primero se calculan las hojas: <m:math><m:mi>H</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>. Luego, como cada resma contiene <m:math><m:mn>500</m:mn></m:math> hojas, la cantidad de resmas es <m:math><m:mn>9&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math>. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>1,5</m:mn></m:math> resmas no alcanza.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">18 resmas<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Al reemplazar <m:math><m:mi>e</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn></m:math> en la fórmula, se obtiene <m:math><m:mi>H</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> hojas. Como cada resma tiene <m:math><m:mn>500</m:mn></m:math> hojas, se necesitan <m:math><m:mn>9&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math> resmas. Esa es la cantidad mínima exacta.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">0,125 resmas<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Con <m:math><m:mi>e</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn></m:math>, la cantidad total de hojas es <m:math><m:mi>H</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>. Luego, al dividir por <m:math><m:mn>500</m:mn></m:math> hojas por resma, resulta <m:math><m:mn>9&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math> resmas. Por eso, <m:math><m:mn>0,125</m:mn></m:math> resmas no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Calcular la cantidad total de hojas</strong></p>
            <p>La fórmula dada es <m:math><m:mi>H</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mi>e</m:mi></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Como se deben imprimir <m:math><m:mn>750</m:mn></m:math> ejemplares, reemplazamos <m:math><m:mi>e</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>H</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9&#160;000</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces se necesitan <strong>9 000 hojas</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Convertir hojas a resmas</strong></p>
            <p>Cada resma contiene <m:math><m:mn>500</m:mn></m:math> hojas.</p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, la cantidad de resmas necesarias es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>9&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Interpretar el resultado</strong></p>
            <p>Como el resultado es exacto, se necesitan exactamente <strong>18 resmas</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La cantidad mínima de resmas de papel que se necesita es <strong>18 resmas</strong>, correspondiente a la <strong>alternativa C</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>